title: New goals to improve Indigenous health (Department of Health - Australian Government)
text: ( Source : Department of Health - Australian Government ) 22 October , 2015 Minister for Rural Health Fiona Nash has launched an Implementation Plan to help Close the Gap by improving the health of Aboriginal and Torres Strait Islander peoples.
